PROJETO-DE-PESQUISA.DESCRICAO-DO-PROJETO:
The main results planned in the project are: 

a conceptual framework with associated formal and best practice techniques that can be used for the design of services; 
techniques for representing semantic descriptions of run-time resources and information, such as user context, service capabilities, user profiles and provider profiles; 
a service design and service architecture definition methodology; 
an integrated software tool to support design operations and analysis of design results (both behaviour models and semantic descriptions); 
case studies in which the above mentioned results are applied and evaluated, in cooperation with other projects within the Freeband Communication programme.
